data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5000 TOWARDS BUYER CLOSING COSTS!!*VA ASSUMABLE LOAN FOR QUALIFIED VA BUYER* If you have been considering a home in Jacksonville NC, come take a look at this listing in Carolina Plantation. This home has 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and just under 3000 sqft. The first floor offers a formal sitting room, formal dining room with a coffered ceiling, half bathroom, living room with a fireplace, large kitchen with lots of cabinet spaces, stainless steel appliances and a large kitchen nook. LVP flooring all throughout the first floor. The second floor offers the primary bedroom and bath suite, three remaining bedrooms, main bathroom and the laundry room. The primary suite provides a ton of space with a trey ceiling and a ceiling fan. The primary suite bathroom has a separate walk-in shower and a soaker tub, dual vanities, sitting area and a large walk-in closet. One of the three bedrooms is a large over the garage room. The property has a covered front porch and a covered back patio. The back yard has a newly installed privacy fence. Nicely designed walkways to the fireplace and covered pergola sitting area. Two car attached garage. Property is located within minutes of area shopping, restaurants and amenities. Area bases Camp Lejeune and New River Air Station within 10 to 20 miles of the property. ADT SECURITY SYSTEM, WASHER & DRYER AND RING DOORBELL AND CAMERAS CONVEY. TV MOUNTS DO NOT CONVEY. **SELLER HAS A VA LOAN THAT COULD BE ASSUMED BY A QUALIFIED VA BUYER. INQUIRE WITH YOUR AGENT FOR MORE DETAILS. **
